 invoking the\nrecovery control, fault estimation and isolation imperfections and\nunreliabilities under different control recovery scenarios.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 28 Aug 2015 02:53:37 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 20 Jun 2016 04:18:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-06-21"}
