nduced background study and reduction. It\nconsists of a Water Cherenkov detector and a Top Tracker system. The readout\nsystem, the detector control system and the offline system insure efficient and\nstable data acquisition and processing.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 28 Aug 2015 10:56:54 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 28 Sep 2015 07:39:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-09-29"}
