ely easier for software programmers who is new to hardware, but with the\nprice of more resources usage on FPGA for similar hardware accelerator\ngeneration.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 28 Aug 2015 08:59:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-09-02"}
